      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for checking out my listing. I\u2019m honestly so excited to find a new home for this beauty! It is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and there isn't a single flaw to be found inside or out. It drives like a dream and is totally ready for its next adventure. You really have to see it in person to appreciate how pristine it is. Feel free to message me with any questions at all\u2014I'd love to chat!",
