    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3 in impeccable condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers crisp engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution. Mechanically flawless, the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the rod bearing service is fully documented. Riding on staggered Style 67 wheels with a pristine chassis, this vehicle maintains its factory-spec suspension geometry and elective damping characteristics. A concours-level specimen for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
