    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true 'time capsule' specimen, presented in showroom-grade condition. The exterior retains its original factory paint, boasting a deep, mirror-like luster free of rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings, thanks to life spent in a climate-controlled garage and a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the premium leather bolsters show no signs of entry wear, the dashboard is crack-free, and every electronic component\u2014from the infotainment system to the ambient lighting\u2014functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It has been maintained with an open-checkbook policy, documented by a comprehensive binder of service records from authorized dealerships. The engine bay is detailed and spotless, and the undercarriage remains remarkably clean. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is a rare opportunity to acquire an unmolested, investment-grade example that drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom floor.",
      "price": 48500.0,
